data.description:
Exquisite Gem in the Heart of Vincenz Cove!
Welcome to this exceptional 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath single family residence in the highly coveted neighborhood of Vincenz Cove, Gilbert. Perfectly situated just half a mile from the bustling Santan Village Mall and with easy access to the 202 Loop, this is an opportunity you won't want to miss.
Step inside this elegant two-story 1,692-square-foot home, which features a roomy two-car garage for your convenience. The moment you walk through the door, you'll be captivated by the charm of the kitchen, complete with sleek black stainless-steel appliances. On the ground floor, you'll also find a handy half bath.
As you ascend the stairs, you'll discover all three bedrooms, conveniently located near the laundry room for your comfort. The master suite boasts a spacious walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom with double sinks, ensuring your personal oasis.

The allure continues outside, where a private covered patio sets the stage for unforgettable gatherings and delightful barbeques. Your guests will be enchanted by the serene atmosphere.

Community amenities abound, including a heated pool and spa for your relaxation, along with a fun-filled children's playground and park.

You'll appreciate the recent updates, with the exterior freshly painted in 2022, and the interior receiving a tasteful makeover in 2023. New fans and light fixtures were thoughtfully installed, as well as brand-new faucets in every bathroom and the kitchen.

This home isn't just a house; it's an opportunity to embrace a family-oriented lifestyle with convenience. Don't miss your chance to make it yours.
